Module com.example.form
Package org.uwo.cs2212.model

Class FloorMap

java.lang.Object
org.uwo.cs2212.model.FloorMap
public class FloorMap extends Object
This class is used to store data on the floor map for a base map. This includes the name, file name, if the legend is shown, and it's position, the list of layers, the config (json) file name, and the corresponding userLayer.
Author:
Yaopeng Xie
